729267f-a.title: Richmond: Park Avenue - Bennett Street
729267f-a.text:
Park Avenue (formerly Broadway), west side, south
from Bennett Street. On the corner of Vreeland Street is
the Park Baptist Chnrch.
About 1910
By Mulford Simonson
From P. L. Sperr Collection
